Mempool Monitor → New Tx → BlockGPT Pipeline:
1. Decode tx → execution trace tokens [T1,T2,...,Tn]
2. Score: S = -∑log P(Ti|history)  
3. Rank: Top-10 highest S → "abnormal"
4. Alert if S > threshold (calibrated 1% FPR)
5. Defense: Pause contract interaction

Performance: 2284 tx/s → covers Ethereum + Solana mempools